@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vwqpsd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (v0 - v2)
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.sin(0.59))
    v0 = (0.09 / (0.30 / v1))
    v2 = 0.50
    v1 = (v1 + (wp.cos(v0 + 0.69) - (v1 + 0.01 * tmp + 0.42)))
    data[tid] = v0
